00:11:16.625 --> 00:11:19.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizás en tus visitas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>conociste a Heiji Shindo.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:11:20.583 --> 00:11:22.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quizá te puso una mano encima.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:11:23.625 --> 00:11:27.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si fue su mano derecha,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>considérate vengada.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:11:28.291 --> 00:11:30.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Brindas servicios.</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:11:31.541 --> 00:11:32.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo también.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:11:40.625 --> 00:11:42.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cuál es tu deseo?</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:11:49.833 --> 00:11:54.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conforme a la ley, la venganza es un lujo</c.bg_transparent>
