114
00:11:55.541 --> 00:11:59.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Las mujeres como yo debemos ser prácticas.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:11:59.333 --> 00:12:01.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Concentrarnos en el resultado.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:12:02.041 --> 00:12:04.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esa casa de apuestas</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>pertenece al Jefe Hamata.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:12:05.375 --> 00:12:08.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Todo pertenece al Jefe Hamata.</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:12:10.208 --> 00:12:13.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Él y su Ejército de las Mil Garras.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:12:24.166 --> 00:12:26.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La mitad de lo que ganamos es suyo.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:12:31.166 --> 00:12:33.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>A veces, pide más.</i></c.bg_transparent>

121
00:12:40.833 --> 00:12:42.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Cualquiera que lo desafíe</i></c.bg_transparent>

122
00:12:42.625 --> 00:12:47.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>es alcanzado por las Mil Garras,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>que destruyen todo lo que ama.</i></c.bg_transparent>

123
00:12:52.541 --> 00:12:57.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hace seis meses,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>el Jefe Hamata se llevó a Kinuyo.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:13:02.500 --> 00:13:06.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Compré a Kinuyo de su padre,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>que se había cansado de abusar de ella.</i></c.bg_transparent>

125
00:13:07.208 --> 00:13:11.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>No sabía nada de su hija,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>excepto que era sordomuda.</i></c.bg_transparent>

126
00:13:13.083 --> 00:13:16.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>No tenía idea</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>de que había un mundo en su interior.</i></c.bg_transparent>

127
00:13:42.958 --> 00:13:45.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Con el tiempo, empezó a confiar en mí.</i></c.bg_transparent>

128
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:58.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Me dijo que prefería morir antes</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>que ser tocada por un hombre otra vez.</i></c.bg_transparent>

129
00:13:58.666 --> 00:14:01.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Le prometí que ningún hombre la tocaría.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:14:03.333 --> 00:14:06.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pero al Jefe Hamata</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>le gusta quebrar cosas delicadas,</i></c.bg_transparent>

131
00:14:06.916 --> 00:14:08.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>así que se la llevó.</i></c.bg_transparent>

132
00:14:12.125 --> 00:14:13.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Me la robó.</i></c.bg_transparent>

133
00:14:15.125 --> 00:14:16.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se lo prometí.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:14:26.833 --> 00:14:30.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo hay una forma de salvar a Kinuyo.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:14:31.000 --> 00:14:32.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quieres que mate a Hamata.</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:14:33.750 --> 00:14:34.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No.</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:14:35.166 --> 00:14:36.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A ella.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:14:38.416 --> 00:14:40.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saben que amo a Kinuyo.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:14:41.375 --> 00:14:44.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si algo le pasara al Jefe Hamata</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>o a ella,</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:14:44.625 --> 00:14:48.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>el Ejército de Mil Garras</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>mataría a todas las almas a mi cuidado.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:14:49.500 --> 00:14:51.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debe parecer que fue un accidente.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:14:52.250 --> 00:14:53.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Así será.</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:14:53.541 --> 00:14:55.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No puede haber testigos.</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:14:56.041 --> 00:14:57.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Seré como el humo.</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:14:57.875 --> 00:14:59.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Júralo.</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:15:00.166 --> 00:15:01.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo juro.</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:15:06.625 --> 00:15:09.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando lo hagas,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>te diré lo que quieres saber.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:15:13.875 --> 00:15:16.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Puedes dormir aquí hasta que sea la hora.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:15:16.458 --> 00:15:17.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ningún ojo te mirará.</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:15:18.708 --> 00:15:20.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Te puedo ofrecer algo?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:15:20.291 --> 00:15:21.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo privacidad.</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:15:25.458 --> 00:15:28.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Antes de que le abras la puerta al cielo,</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:15:28.291 --> 00:15:31.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>quiero que mires a Kinuyo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y le hagas la señal.</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:15:34.625 --> 00:15:37.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ella sabrá que tu mano es la mía,</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:15:37.500 --> 00:15:39.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y estará en paz.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:16:03.250 --> 00:16:04.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Ringo?</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:16:04.458 --> 00:16:05.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Puedo servirte?</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:16:06.125 --> 00:16:08.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dije que no quiero compañía.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:16:08.708 --> 00:16:12.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por favor. Si no me dejas entrar,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Madame me pegará.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:16:50.250 --> 00:16:51.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Akemi?</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:16:52.541 --> 00:16:54.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cuántos días llevas orando?</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:16:54.583 --> 00:16:58.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No agotes a los dioses con peticiones.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Espera a que sea necesario.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:17:02.583 --> 00:17:06.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enójate conmigo todo lo que quieras.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Iremos a Edo en dos días.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:17:07.958 --> 00:17:10.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debes estar lista para casarte,</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:17:10.750 --> 00:17:12.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y para estar casada.</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:17:12.666 --> 00:17:15.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tu madre te habría enseñado</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>como ser una buena esposa.</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:17:15.875 --> 00:17:19.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ella no era ideal.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Me respondía mucho, como tú, pero…</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:17:19.916 --> 00:17:21.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>sabía cómo complacerme.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:17:25.625 --> 00:17:27.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Las series de 12 y 20 posiciones.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:17:27.916 --> 00:17:31.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una esposa debería conocer las 12.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Las 20 son para profesionales.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:17:31.791 --> 00:17:34.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero formarás parte del sogunato, así que…</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:17:41.541 --> 00:17:44.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Akemi, en algún momento</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tendrás que hablar conmigo.</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:17:48.041 --> 00:17:50.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿A dónde pudo haber ido?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- No tengo idea.</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:17:54.708 --> 00:17:56.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Encuentren a mi hija!</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:18:11.833 --> 00:18:13.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nunca lo he visto.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:18:13.625 --> 00:18:14.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Esposo?</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:18:19.833 --> 00:18:22.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vamos. Este lugar es muy ordinario.</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:18:22.291 --> 00:18:23.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es Mihonoseki.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:18:23.875 --> 00:18:25.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Querías trabajar aquí.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:18:25.708 --> 00:18:28.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿No quieres ganar más dinero?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Busquemos algo mejor.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:18:39.541 --> 00:18:40.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Busquemos algo mejor.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:48.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Busquemos algo mejor.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:19:05.208 --> 00:19:06.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debemos irnos. Ahora.</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:19:06.541 --> 00:19:08.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bien, un pueblo más.</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:19:08.333 --> 00:19:09.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por aquí. Lo sé.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:19:20.291 --> 00:19:23.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. Ese es el camino más largo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Por la costa.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:19:24.625 --> 00:19:27.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por aquí tendremos suerte.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Tengo un presentimiento.</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:19:29.916 --> 00:19:32.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Taigen, ¿dónde estás?</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:19:35.291 --> 00:19:37.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te golpeará con el puño.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:19:40.375 --> 00:19:42.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te golpeará con un garrote.</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:19:44.875 --> 00:19:46.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te golpeará con…</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:19:46.916 --> 00:19:47.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>un martillo.</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:20:00.708 --> 00:20:02.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Esto es aburrido.</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:20:04.041 --> 00:20:05.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estoy aburrido.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:20:06.208 --> 00:20:07.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me gusta.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:20:08.541 --> 00:20:12.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me dirás todo lo que sabes sobre Mizu.</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:20:16.250 --> 00:20:19.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay una razón por la que no bajo aquí</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>desde hace una década.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:20:20.458 --> 00:20:22.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te esperaré para la cena.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:20:28.333 --> 00:20:29.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te humilló.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:20:30.583 --> 00:20:33.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Arruinó tu matrimonio</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>con el Clan Tokunobu.</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:20:34.208 --> 00:20:37.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué sufrir tanto</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para proteger a un enemigo?</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:20:39.875 --> 00:20:41.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Se merece algo mejor que tú.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:20:44.500 --> 00:20:46.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te cortará con un cuchillo.</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:21:17.291 --> 00:21:19.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nunca les pedí que construyeran esto.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:21:19.708 --> 00:21:25.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Supusieron que el hombre blanco necesitaba</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una capilla. La pusieron junto a la celda.</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:21:26.500 --> 00:21:27.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No somos amigos.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:21:28.291 --> 00:21:30.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hace tiempo que no hablo contigo.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:34.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No te deshonraría pidiéndote un favor.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:21:35.791 --> 00:21:40.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero creo que hay algo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que puedo hacer por ti.</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:21:41.500 --> 00:21:44.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Aquí son impíos desde siempre.</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:21:44.250 --> 00:21:47.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Viste lo que les hicieron</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a tus sacerdotes y fieles.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:21:47.333 --> 00:21:53.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Fueron expulsados y crucificados,</c.bg_transparent>
