213
00:21:53.833 --> 00:21:55.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Los japoneses son paganos.</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:21:55.916 --> 00:21:58.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por suerte para ti, su líder es codicioso.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:21:59.500 --> 00:22:02.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Planeo cortarle la cabeza a ese sogún</c.bg_transparent>

