00:22:02.083 --> 00:22:06.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y reimaginar esta nación más a mi agrado.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:22:07.166 --> 00:22:10.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Suelo creer que mis planes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>te resultan indiferentes.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:22:11.208 --> 00:22:14.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Entiendo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A mí me resultan indiferentes los tuyos.</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:22:14.916 --> 00:22:16.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero te diré algo.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:22:16.708 --> 00:22:19.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si mis planes llegan a buen puerto,</c.bg_transparent>

