00:22:19.916 --> 00:22:23.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>lo tomaré como una señal</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:22:23.791 --> 00:22:27.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>de que interviniste</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para que el viento soplara a mi favor,</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:22:27.458 --> 00:22:29.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y, en retribución,</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:22:29.875 --> 00:22:32.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>construiré un púlpito en mi nuevo dominio</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:22:33.333 --> 00:22:37.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>y convocaré a tus sacerdotes</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para que propaguen tu palabra,</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:22:38.041 --> 00:22:42.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>y te entregaré</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>una nación entera de almas.</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:22:44.125 --> 00:22:46.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como agradecimiento,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>si lo consideras oportuno.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:22:47.625 --> 00:22:49.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>A mí me da igual.</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:22:52.708 --> 00:22:56.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Las almas no me sirven para nada.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:23:03.875 --> 00:23:06.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Por aquí, por allá. Nada le viene bien.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:10.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Muy húmedo, muy seco, muy hediondo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿Por qué le hago caso?</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:23:10.500 --> 00:23:13.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cuando las chicas hablan,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>les doy una gota de esto.</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:23:14.125 --> 00:23:15.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bendito silencio.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:23:15.750 --> 00:23:19.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Despiertan en su nuevo hogar</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y Goro cuenta su fortuna.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:23:19.500 --> 00:23:20.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero con Akemi,</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:23:21.000 --> 00:23:23.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>solo respeto y moderación.</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:23:23.125 --> 00:23:24.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Goro?</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:23:24.500 --> 00:23:27.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Perdóname.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Sabes que estaría perdida sin ti.</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:23:28.583 --> 00:23:30.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué son unos pueblos más juntos?</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:23:30.666 --> 00:23:32.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Vamos, es la hora!</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:23:34.166 --> 00:23:37.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Vamos, no me perderé el duelo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>por ustedes! ¡Quiero ver sangre!</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:23:38.041 --> 00:23:40.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- ¿Un duelo?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Un flacucho y un grandote.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:23:40.500 --> 00:23:44.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apuesto cinco </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>mons </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>al flacucho,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>tiene cara de demonio.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:23:44.500 --> 00:23:45.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un demonio.</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:23:47.833 --> 00:23:49.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El pueblo que buscamos.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:24:03.708 --> 00:24:05.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nos perdimos la sangre.</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:24:12.791 --> 00:24:15.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Taigen. Es su bufanda.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:24:18.250 --> 00:24:19.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un demonio.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:24:38.416 --> 00:24:39.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hallé el burdel indicado.</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:24:42.791 --> 00:24:45.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, el de Madame Kaji no.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:24:45.791 --> 00:24:48.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debes estar con las cortesanas. Elegancia.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:24:49.583 --> 00:24:52.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Este es conocido por sus peculiaridades.</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:24:55.416 --> 00:24:56.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bueno.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:25:09.625 --> 00:25:10.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Goro!</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:25:10.750 --> 00:25:13.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No! ¡Fuera! ¡Largo de aquí!</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:25:14.125 --> 00:25:16.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué clase de bienvenida es esta?</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:25:16.708 --> 00:25:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡No eres bienvenido!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>No desde tu última venta.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:25:20.125 --> 00:25:22.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madame Kaji ni mirará a una chica tuya.</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:25:22.958 --> 00:25:25.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mirará a esta.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:25:59.041 --> 00:26:00.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pagará una fortuna por ti.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:26:00.875 --> 00:26:04.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Siempre quise ser rico.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>¿Te imaginas?</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:26:04.500 --> 00:26:06.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo se sentirá?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:26:08.708 --> 00:26:11.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dejas de pensar en lo que rico que eres.</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:26:18.041 --> 00:26:19.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Madame Kaji, yo…</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:26:19.333 --> 00:26:21.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué fue lo último que te dije, Goro?</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:26:22.250 --> 00:26:24.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>"Si me vuelves a hablar,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>te romperé la nariz".</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:26:25.000 --> 00:26:29.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si podemos dejar de lado la violencia</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un momento, quisiera presentarte…</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:26:29.833 --> 00:26:30.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>a Akemi.</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:26:31.583 --> 00:26:33.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cortesana venerada de Gion.</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:26:33.875 --> 00:26:36.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Digna de la realeza.</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:26:36.541 --> 00:26:39.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Sus pies…</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Ya hay una chica que actúa de princesa.</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:26:39.708 --> 00:26:41.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No como Akemi.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:26:42.291 --> 00:26:45.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Experta en canto, baile, caligrafía, </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>koto</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>.</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:26:45.833 --> 00:26:49.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es capaz de debatir los </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>sutras</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>como el monje Takuan.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:26:50.416 --> 00:26:54.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es una de tus viudas arruinadas,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>amantes de la noche o adictas al té.</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:26:56.500 --> 00:26:58.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Pose favorita de tu cliente más rico?</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:27:00.583 --> 00:27:01.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo arriba.</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:27:02.625 --> 00:27:03.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Goro</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>,</i></c.bg_transparent>

279
00:27:04.041 --> 00:27:07.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>debo reconocerte que eres consistente.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:27:07.750 --> 00:27:10.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres un idiota todos los días de tu vida.</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:27:10.291 --> 00:27:13.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Te engañó. Si ella es una cortesana,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yo soy una doncella.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:27:14.208 --> 00:27:16.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres de alta alcurnia, ¿verdad?</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:27:16.625 --> 00:27:20.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una princesa de verdad bañada en leche.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:27:20.541 --> 00:27:21.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Virgen.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Yo…</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:27:21.583 --> 00:27:23.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Has visto dos pitos en toda tu vida.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:27:28.125 --> 00:27:32.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero tu inexperiencia puede ser</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>un signo de belleza, no una verruga…</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:27:32.666 --> 00:27:33.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>si quieres trabajar.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:27:34.458 --> 00:27:35.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero hacerlo.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:27:36.291 --> 00:27:37.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo haré.</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:27:38.041 --> 00:27:41.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es una residencia de lujo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para bailar y conversar.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:27:41.791 --> 00:27:47.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo que la geisha intenta evitar de noche</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>es nuestra labor diaria. A nadie le gusta.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:27:47.583 --> 00:27:50.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pero si puedes sobrellevarlo,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>yo te cuidaré.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:27:51.083 --> 00:27:55.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Goro, 50 </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>ryos </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>por tu princesa virgen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>si se desempeña adecuadamente esta noche.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:27:56.041 --> 00:27:57.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una prueba.</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:27:57.625 --> 00:27:59.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ven por la mañana a buscar…</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:27:59.333 --> 00:28:00.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>tu dinero…</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:28:00.708 --> 00:28:02.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>o a tu chica.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:28:02.708 --> 00:28:06.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Que la diosa Benzaiten</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>guíe tus manos y esos pies.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:28:07.583 --> 00:28:10.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí, niña.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Así de fácil te compraron y vendieron.</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:28:11.041 --> 00:28:12.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Rápido como un matrimonio.</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:28:12.666 --> 00:28:14.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mi nombre es Akemi.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:28:14.500 --> 00:28:17.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Me molestaré en recordarlo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>si sigues aquí mañana.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:28:19.208 --> 00:28:21.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tu primera prueba, come.</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:28:22.208 --> 00:28:23.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O serás comida.</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:28:31.500 --> 00:28:34.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ella es Akemi, una noble de alta alcurnia.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:28:35.166 --> 00:28:37.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Más que maquillaje y afectación, como Ise.</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:28:38.875 --> 00:28:42.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya se arrepiente de haber escapado</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>del castillo de su papá.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:28:42.750 --> 00:28:43.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Para nada.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:28:44.500 --> 00:28:46.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Quiero encontrar un cliente.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:28:50.250 --> 00:28:54.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Toma, un vestido viejo de Ise.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Está roto, pero si lo cubres, no se nota.</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:28:55.208 --> 00:28:56.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Así se usa ahora?</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:28:56.791 --> 00:28:58.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es la última moda en Kioto.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:29:00.375 --> 00:29:02.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Terminen de acicalarse y salgan.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:29:03.958 --> 00:29:07.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hay cuatro hombres aún vestidos</c.bg_transparent>
