<c.bg_transparent>porque le había arruinado el compromiso.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:35:56.541 --> 00:35:59.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Estaba más enojado por su pelo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que por su boda.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:36:00.750 --> 00:36:02.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Cómo se llamaba?</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:36:04.541 --> 00:36:05.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No me acuerdo.</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:36:07.291 --> 00:36:08.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En fin. Está muerto.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:36:09.000 --> 00:36:10.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué?</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:36:10.583 --> 00:36:12.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sí. Lo maté.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:36:21.208 --> 00:36:22.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es buena.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:36:24.166 --> 00:36:25.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Suéltame!</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:36:25.333 --> 00:36:26.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Quítate!</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:36:26.750 --> 00:36:28.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Crees que no te recuerdo?</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:36:28.750 --> 00:36:30.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>La princesa Akemi del Clan Tokunobu.</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:36:31.458 --> 00:36:32.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Envenenaste mi bebida.</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:36:33.541 --> 00:36:34.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Ojalá fuera veneno!</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:36:35.458 --> 00:36:36.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¡Taigen!</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:36:38.916 --> 00:36:39.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya cállate.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:36:40.666 --> 00:36:41.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No lo maté.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:36:42.125 --> 00:36:44.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo dejé vivir</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y firmamos un contrato para pelear.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:36:45.666 --> 00:36:47.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Está vivo? ¿Dónde?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:36:47.750 --> 00:36:51.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Viniste hasta aquí</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para salvar un compromiso arruinado?</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:36:53.125 --> 00:36:57.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tu padre probablemente encontró</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a un noble jovencito para reemplazarlo.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:36:58.625 --> 00:36:59.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>El hijo del sogún.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:37:01.416 --> 00:37:04.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Las mujeres en este mundo</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no tienen ninguna opción buena.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:37:05.041 --> 00:37:06.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excepto tú.</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:37:06.666 --> 00:37:08.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Como una criatura mágica del bosque,</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:37:09.041 --> 00:37:11.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>podrías tener lo que quisieras,</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:37:11.666 --> 00:37:14.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>y en vez de eso suplicas comer basura.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:37:21.125 --> 00:37:22.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tienes a una chica.</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:37:23.083 --> 00:37:24.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Una chica linda.</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:37:24.916 --> 00:37:26.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Espera. ¿Cuál es el plan?</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:37:27.041 --> 00:37:28.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No es una chica.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:37:28.541 --> 00:37:30.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es una princesa.</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:37:30.083 --> 00:37:33.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Es la princesa de Taigen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>y trató de matarme.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:37:34.833 --> 00:37:36.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si grita, mátala.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:37:37.166 --> 00:37:39.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Si se mueve, mátala.</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:37:39.625 --> 00:37:41.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué? No puedo matarla.</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:37:41.416 --> 00:37:43.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué crees que hace un aprendiz?</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:37:56.041 --> 00:37:57.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Tienes que mirarme fijo?</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:37:58.375 --> 00:37:59.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo siento.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:38:08.041 --> 00:38:11.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>La casa de apuestas de Hamata</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>está atiborrada de Mil Garras.</i></c.bg_transparent>

463
00:38:11.750 --> 00:38:14.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Nunca pierde de vista a Kinuyo.</i></c.bg_transparent>

464
00:38:14.250 --> 00:38:16.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Excepto cuando viene el doctor cada mañana</i></c.bg_transparent>

465
00:38:16.916 --> 00:38:19.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>a tratarle las llagas</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>que el propio Hamata le causó.</i></c.bg_transparent>

466
00:38:21.500 --> 00:38:24.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Incluso entonces,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>su leal guardaespaldas vigila.</i></c.bg_transparent>

467
00:41:38.333 --> 00:41:39.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yo te protegeré.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:43:03.375 --> 00:43:07.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Corre a decirles a los guardias nocturnos</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>que hubo una pelea.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:43:07.083 --> 00:43:08.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dos personas.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:43:09.000 --> 00:43:09.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Me oyes, niño?</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:43:10.000 --> 00:43:11.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Al portal. ¡Ve!</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:43:30.125 --> 00:43:32.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Le hiciste la seña?</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:43:36.500 --> 00:43:37.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Qué seña hizo ella?</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:43:39.416 --> 00:43:40.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Lo entendió.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:43:46.500 --> 00:43:48.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>En el punto más distante,</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:43:48.250 --> 00:43:51.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>antes de que la roca se haga costa,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hay un pozo.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:43:51.291 --> 00:43:55.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Cien pasos al norte,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hay una puerta cubierta por la marea.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:43:55.416 --> 00:43:57.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Conduce a un túnel bajo el mar</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:43:58.000 --> 00:44:00.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>que da al vientre del castillo de Fowler.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:44:02.041 --> 00:44:03.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Duerme todo el día.</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:44:03.916 --> 00:44:05.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Luego ve y muere.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:44:17.125 --> 00:44:18.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Debería haberte matado.</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:44:18.791 --> 00:44:22.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ese fue mi error.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Quería conocerte primero.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:44:22.291 --> 00:44:25.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Para ver qué poder ejerces sobre Taigen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>para alejarlo de mí.</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:44:26.458 --> 00:44:29.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Bajo tu máscara,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>no eres el asesino que finges.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:44:37.000 --> 00:44:37.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Vete.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:44:39.791 --> 00:44:41.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pensé que serías especial.</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:44:42.458 --> 00:44:44.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tu cara ni da tanto miedo.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:44:44.708 --> 00:44:45.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Solo estás…</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:44:46.583 --> 00:44:47.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>enojado.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:44:48.416 --> 00:44:50.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ya veo por qué le gustas.</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:44:50.500 --> 00:44:52.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eres como Taigen cuando éramos niños.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:44:53.250 --> 00:44:54.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Un mocoso de mierda.</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:44:55.125 --> 00:44:56.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>¿Lo conocías?</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:45:04.958 --> 00:45:05.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Niño.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:45:19.125 --> 00:45:21.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maten a todos. Luego préndanlo fuego.</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:46:10.500 --> 00:46:12.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Subtítulos: Ezequiel Schmoller</c.bg_transparent>

